|offstyle  = 陛下
|altstyle  = 太皇陛下（2004年—）<br>亲王殿下（1955年—1993年）}}
西哈努克一生中因持有许多正式和非正式的头衔而闻名，<ref>Osborne (1994), p. 3.</ref>[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]将其列为拥有各种国家及政治公职数量最多的王室成员。<ref name="Narong342">Narong (2007), p. 342.</ref>1941年西哈努克即位为王时使用的正式头衔是“诺罗敦·西哈努克·瓦尔曼国王”（{{lang|km|ព្រះបាទសម្តេចព្រះ នរោត្តម សីហនុ វរ្ម័ន}}，Preah Bat Samdech Preah Norodom Sihanouk Varman），此头衔于1941年至1955年间使用，1993年至2004年再度使用。<ref name="Jeldres54" />1955年退位后恢复了亲王头衔，同年，其父[[诺罗敦·苏拉玛里特|诺罗敦·苏拉玛里特]]授予他“{{lang|km|សម្តេចព្រះ[[:wikt:ឧបយុវរាជ|ឧបយុវរាជ]]}}”（Samdech Preah Upayuvareach）之头衔，<ref name="Jeldres61" />此头衔字面意思上是“年轻的[[副王_(东南亚)|副王]]”，实为授予逊位国王的头衔。<ref>Osborne (1994), p. 92.</ref>自20世纪六十年代初开始，西哈努克担任国家元首，<ref>Chandler (1991), p. 121.</ref>被大多数柬埔寨人亲切地称为“亲王父亲”<ref name="renminribao19730305"/>（{{lang|km|សម្តេចឪ}}，Samdech Euv）。<ref name="Narong342" /><ref>Jeldres (2005), p. 194.</ref>

2004年第二次退位后，西哈努克被称为柬埔寨“王父”（{{lang|km|ព្រះមហាវីរក្សត្រ}}，Preah Mâha Viraksat），<ref>Widyono (2008), p. 280.</ref>中华人民共和国将其译为“[[太上皇|太皇]]”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cctv.com/2012/10/17/VIDEkRqklB4jjRDe14xNJUwC121017.shtml|title=[视频]新闻人物：柬埔寨太皇西哈努克|author=央视网|date=2018年11月21日|accessdate=2019年6月17日|archive-date=2019年6月17日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617161110/http://news.cctv.com/2012/10/17/VIDEkRqklB4jjRDe14xNJUwC121017.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>官方正式头衔为{{lang|km|ព្រះករុណាព្រះបាទសម្តេចព្រះ នរោត្តម សីហនុ ព្រះមហាវីរក្សត្រ}}（Preah Karuna Preah Bat Sâmdach Preah Norodom Sihanouk Preahmâhaviraksat）。<ref name="Narong342" />他也被以另一个荣衔进行称呼：“诺罗敦·西哈努克国王陛下，伟大的英雄国王，高棉独立、领土完整及国家统一的王父”（{{lang|km|ព្រះករុណា ព្រះបាទសម្ដេចព្រះ នរោត្តម សីហនុ ព្រះមហាវីរក្សត្រ ព្រះវររាជបិតាឯករាជ្យ បូរណភាពទឹកដី និងឯកភាពជាតិខ្មែរ}}）。<ref>{{cite web|author=Post Staff|url=http://www.akp.gov.kh/kh/?p=43382|title=ព្រះករុណាព្រះបាទសម្តេចព្រះ នរោត្តម សីហនុ ព្រះមហាវីរក្សត្រ ព្រះវររាជបិតាឯករាជ្យ បូរណភាពទឹកដី និងឯកភាពជាតិខ្មែរ ព្រះអង្គបានយាងចូលព្រះទីវង្គត|date=2012-10-15|accessdate=2015-07-13|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6b666GYqO?url=http://www.akp.gov.kh/kh/?p=43382|archivedate=2015-08-27|work=Agence Kampuchea Presse|deadurl=yes}}</ref>与此同时，他发布一项王室法令，要求称呼自己为“亲王祖父”（{{lang|km|សម្ដេចតា}}，Samdech Ta）或“亲王曾祖父”（{{lang|km|សម្ដេចតាទួត}}，Samdech Ta-tuot）。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Lor Chandara|author2=Wency Leung|lastauthoramp=yes|url=https://www.cambodiadaily.com/archives/abdication-wont-diminish-kings-influence-43261/|title=Abdication Won't Diminish King's Influence|date=2004-10-14|accessdate=2015-07-21|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bGboqStU?url=https://www.cambodiadaily.com/archives/abdication-wont-diminish-kings-influence-43261/|archivedate=2015-09-03|work=The Cambodia Daily|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Cabinet of Prime Minister Hun Sen|url=http://cnv.org.kh/selected-impromptu-comments-during-the-meeting-and-handing-out-of-land-titles-to-people-in-the-communes-of-roen-and-tbeng-lej-of-siemreaps-banteay-srey-district/|title=Selected Impromptu Comments during the Meeting and Handing out of land titles to People in the Communes of Roen and Tbeng Lej of Siemreap's Banteay Srey District|date=2012-11-12|accessdate=2015-07-21|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bGbqnSdO?url=http://cnv.org.kh/selected-impromptu-comments-during-the-meeting-and-handing-out-of-land-titles-to-people-in-the-communes-of-roen-and-tbeng-lej-of-siemreaps-banteay-srey-district/|archivedate=2015-09-03|work=Cambodia New Vision|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2012年10月西哈努克逝世后，他被[[诺罗敦·西哈莫尼|西哈莫尼国王]]追谥为“躺在钻石瓮中的诺罗敦·西哈努克国王”（{{lang|km|ព្រះករុណាព្រះនរោត្តម សីហនុ ព្រះបរមរតនកោដ្ឋ}}，Preah Karuna Preah Norodom Sihanouk Preah Borom Ratanakkot）。<ref>{{cite web|author=អត្ថបទ អង្គភាពព័ត៌មាន និងប្រតិកម្មរហ័ស (Press and Quick Reaction Unit)|url=http://www.pressocm.gov.kh/site/detailTextshort/3577#.VbC_DmJ9JrA|title=សម្តេចតេជោពន្យល់ពីការប្រើប្រាស់ព្រះបរមបច្ឆាមរណនាមរបស់សម្តេចឪតម្រូវការសព្វាវុធការពារជាតិ និងការកែលម្អលើបញ្ហាការវាស់វែងដីធ្លី|date=2012-11-13|accessdate=2015-07-23|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6b66BcWDd?url=http://www.pressocm.gov.kh/site/detailTextshort/3577#.VbC_DmJ9JrA|archivedate=2015-08-27|work=Office of the Council of Ministers|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

