|Norodom Monineath Sihanouk
|1936年6月18日
|在世
|原名葆拉-莫尼克·伊齐（Paule-Monique Izzi），是一位法国银行家的女儿，具有法国、意大利混血血统。<ref>Jeldres (2005), p. 69.</ref>莫尼克于1955年3月5日结婚，成为“第二夫人”，1968年诺丽亚与西哈努克离婚后，莫尼克后成为了西哈努克唯一的合法伴侣。生二子，皆为婚前私生子，其中一子为后来的国王[[西哈莫尼|西哈莫尼]]。<ref name="RoyArk"/>
|-
|}

=== 子女 ===
西哈努克共有8子6女。其中5个子女和14个孙辈在[[民主柬埔寨|红色高棉政权]]时期失踪，西哈努克推测他们已遭[[红色高棉|红色高棉]]杀害。<ref>Osborne (1994), p. 236.</ref><ref name="TCN">{{cite web|author=Douglas Gillison|url=https://www.cambodiadaily.com/archives/retired-king-says-kr-murdered-his-children-grandchildren-1242/|title=Retired King Says KR Murdered His Children, Grandchildren|date=2008-04-22|accessdate=2015-07-21|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6bGbubWze?url=https://www.cambodiadaily.com/archives/retired-king-says-kr-murdered-his-children-grandchildren-1242/|archivedate=2015-09-03|work=The Cambodia Daily|deadurl=yes}}</ref>西哈努克的儿孙中，[[诺罗敦·尤瓦那|尤瓦那]]的儿子{{link-en|诺罗敦·维查林|Norodom Ekcharin}}曾被推定死亡，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://geneall.net/en/name/2129880/norodom-veakcharin-prince-of-cambodia/, |title=Norodom Veakcharin, prince of Cambodia |accessdate=2019-06-17 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701103023/https://geneall.net/en/name/2129880/norodom-veakcharin-prince-of-cambodia/,/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>事实上经[[泰国|泰国]][[素林府|素林府]]逃往[[瑞典|瑞典]]。后来维查林于2013年归国与家人团聚。<ref name="Jeldres">{{Cite web |url=https://www.phnompenhpost.com/post-life-arts-culture/updated-edition-provides-insight-lives-and-lineage-cambodias-royals |title=Updated edition provides insight into lives and lineage of Cambodia’s royals |accessdate=2019-06-17 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701102954/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/post-life-arts-culture/updated-edition-provides-insight-lives-and-lineage-cambodias-royals |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

